Simulated Data: the Longitudinal Study of Australian Children (LSAC)

LSACdata.Rd

This dataset contains simulated data based on the Longitudinal Study of Australian Children (LSAC). The data comprises 5,107 rows and 11 columns.

Usage

LSACdata

Format

A data.frame with 5,107 rows, containing the following variables:

sep

A binary exposure variable

fam_stress

A binary intermediate confounder

parent_mh

A binary mediator

preschool_att

A binary mediator

child_mh

A binary outcome variable

child_SDQscore

A continuous outcome variable

child_sex

A binary baseline confounder

child_atsi

A binary baseline confounder

mat_cob

A binary baseline confounder

mat_engl

A binary baseline confounder

mat_age

A binary baseline confounder
